Pseudo-BNF
----------

package    = header, file*

file       = pathLength, path, dataLength, data

header     = 'P', 'K', 'G', version
version    = UBYTE      # Must be 0

pathLength = LONG
path       = BYTE[pathLength] 
dataLength = LONG
data       = BYTE[dataLength] 

Example
-------

"PKG", 0, 3L, "foo", 8L, "barbarba"

Note: No NULL bytes after strings!
